name: SeaWire -  Web Wireframe UI Kit
description:
SeaWire - Figma Wireframe Kit for Website


What's new in 1.1

  • Added 4 new categories: About Us, Timeline, Comments, How it Works
  • Over 50+ new design patterns
  • Better design systems
  • Fixed design consistency


SeaWire - Figma Wireframe Kit is modernly crafted Figma wireframe template which can be used for:

  • Wireframing
  • Creating Landing Pages
  • Create prototypes


Fasten your workflow when creating Website designs with SeaWire, no need to make wireframe with manual sketches on paper!


This template consists of 6 pre-made landing pages and 300 pre-made layouts from 19 most popular categories to make your workflow fast and seamless.


Features

  • Using Google Fonts
  • Exclusively made for Figma
  • Visual Hierarchy using 8 px soft grid
  • Organised components
  • Easily change colors with color Styleguide
  • Easily change text style with Typography Styleguide
  • Well organized layers and groups
